can and MRI under PPP mode by March 2018."}, "003-section": {"000-title": "Ama Clinic Yojana \u2013 Urban Health Care Services", "001-normal": "The state govt. will provide high quality services for proper health in urban areas. This yojana will enable the citizens to get fixed-day specialist consultations in obstetrics and gynaecology, paediatrics, medicine, geriatrics, eye care, physiotherapy and psychiatric services. This scheme will benefit around 45 lakh people of the urban areas."}, "004-section": {"000-title": "Anmol Yojana \u2013 Computer Tablets for ANMs", "001-normal": "Govt. also decided to provide Anmol Tablet computers to give Auxiliary Nurse Midwifes (ANMs) access to the latest technology. This will enable ANMs to provide real time services for better helath care services.", "002-normal": "Odisha CM has launched these 4 schemes to provide better health services in the state. This scheme will also help in reducing the Infant Mortality Rate (IMR) and Maternal Mortality Rate (MMR)."}}